Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Since #ComradeKamala took over the border there has been a 43% nationwide increase in violent crime and a 60% increase in rape.In New York this June, an illegal alien released into our country by Kamala Harris approached two 13-year-old children with a machete in broad daylight, forced them into the woods, tied them together by the wrists and raped the young girl at a park.Two Kamala migrants were just arrested for the rape of a 46-year-old woman in Coney Island—throwing her to the ground and raping her with a knife to her throat. One of them had previously been arrested for raping another woman but instead of being deported, he was released.
